DescUsage: <<
The MetaboAnalyst 2.0 server for a particular version of R
is started, for metaboanalyst-tomcat8-r31 package variant
as follows...

1) Start the tomcat server, designated in the package name,
with...

sudo -u tomcat %p/bin/tomcat8 start

...where %p is the fink installation prefix used locally.

2) Start the Rserve R server for the matching version of R
with...

  sudo -u tomcat %p/Library/Frameworks/R.framework/Versions/3.1/Resources/bin/R

and then execute...

  library(Rserve)
  Rserve()

at the R prompt. The terminal window should be left to monitor
for R messages.

3) Access your local copy of MetaboAnalyst at:

   http://localhost:8080/MetaboAnalyst/

<<
